data.description: Fantastic opportunity to be in the boutique community of Carmel at Vanderbilt Lakes! This spacious 3 bedroom plus loft villa also has two and half baths and boasts just over 1800 square feet! Enjoy the gorgeous lake view from the lanai while having that morning coffee. Private, landscaped courtyard. Main floor primary bedroom with private bath that boasts double-sinks, a walk-in shower and a skylight. Bedroom two is upstairs and has it's own private full bath and a loft-sitting area. Bedroom three is on the main floor split from the primary bedroom. Bedroom three can easily double as a home office with it's glass French doors. Close to many popular beaches, shopping, restaurants and minutes from Naples. This double-gated community west of 41 offers significant security and privacy and is minutes from RSW Airport.
